---
title: Cal Smart Turkey Salad with Creamy Dressing and Feta
description: This speedy salad is jam-packed with fresh tomatoes, crunchy carrots and crisp apples, then topped with juicy seared turkey and a  delicious mayo dressing for a wholesome kickstart to your week!

